# Blueprint Asset - Lighting Manager
# Este arquivo representa um Blueprint que herda de ULightingSystemManager
# e fornece interface visual para designers ajustarem a iluminação

[Blueprint Configuration]
Parent Class: ULightingSystemManager
Blueprint Type: Actor Component

[Default Values]
TimeScale: 60.0  # 1 minuto real = 1 hora no jogo
CurrentTimeOfDay: 8.0  # Começar de manhã
AutoAdvanceTime: true
CurrentWeather: Clear
CurrentThreatLevel: Safe

[Exposed Parameters for Level Designers]
- Time of Day Override (0-24 hours)
- Weather State Selection
- Threat Level Override
- Manual Sun Position Control
- Fog Density Multiplier
- Shadow Intensity Override
- Atmosphere Tint Override

[Events]
- OnTimeOfDayChanged
- OnWeatherChanged
- OnThreatLevelChanged
- OnDayNightCycle (Dawn, Day, Dusk, Night transitions)

[Debug Visualization]
- Current Time Display
- Sun Position Indicator
- Weather State HUD
- Threat Level Indicator
- Mood Transition Progress